{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UouSjWLoexuEH21J3HZK7R","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me compile the comprehensive inventory report with all the exact file paths and line numbers.\n\n## Referral System Backend Implementation Inventory\n\n### 1. **Migration: `011_referral.sql`**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql`\n\n**Tables created**:\n- `referral_codes` (lines 8-14) — Player-chosen codes, 3-16 chars [a-z0-9-], one per wallet\n- `referral_links` (lines 17-22) — Immutable referrer→referee binding, one referrer per player\n- `referral_earnings` (lines 28-44) — Per-referee per-round earnings tracking with idempotency guard\n- `referral_claims` (lines 56-68) — Async SOL payout tracking with status tracking\n- `referral_kol_rates` (lines 78-84) — KOL custom referrer rate overrides (admin-set)\n\n**Indexes**: \n- `idx_referral_links_referrer` (line 24)\n- `idx_referral_earnings_referrer` (line 46)\n- `idx_referral_earnings_referee` (line 49)\n- `idx_referral_earnings_round_id` (line 52)\n- `idx_referral_claims_wallet` (line 70)\n- `idx_referral_claims_status` (line 73)\n\n---\n\n### 2. **DB Client Methods (db.ts)**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts`\n\n**Interface Declarations**:\n- `ReferralCode` (lines 130-136)\n- `ReferralLink` (lines 138-143)\n- `ReferralEarning` (lines 145-158)\n- `ReferralStats` (lines 160-167)\n- `ReferralClaim` (lines 169-178)\n\n**Db Interface Methods** (lines 206-419):\n- `insertReferralCode(wallet, code)` — declaration: line 318 | implementation: lines 782-789\n- `getReferralCodeByWallet(wallet)` — declaration: line 321 | implementation: lines 791-796\n- `getReferralCodeByCode(code)` — declaration: line 324 | implementation: lines 798-803\n- `upsertReferralCode(wallet, code)` — declaration: line 327 | implementation: lines 805-815\n- `insertReferralLi