g-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts`\n\n- **Import**: line 17 (`createReferralRoutes`)\n- **Route mounting**: lines 94-99\n  ```\n  app.use(\"/referral/*\", createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }));\n  app.route(\"/referral\", createReferralRoutes({ db, sql, config }));\n  ```\n- **JWT auth middleware applied**: line 97 (all methods required)\n- **Claim handler registration**: lines 181-184\n  ```\n  registerHandler(\n    EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED,\n    createClaimHandler({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair }),\n  );\n  ```\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Settlement Hook: `settle-tx.ts`**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts`\n\n- **`recordReferralEarnings` function**: lines 123-195\n  - Called within transaction in `settleMatch`: line 382 (inside `db.withTransaction`)\n  - Called within transaction in `settleLordRound`: line 595 (inside `db.withTransaction`)\n  \n- **In `settleMatch` (Coinflip)**:\n  - Transaction wrapper: lines 348-392\n  - Referral hook call: lines 382-391\n  - Players passed: lines 387-390 (creator + opponent wagers)\n\n- **In `settleLordRound` (Lord of RNGs)**:\n  - Transaction wrapper: lines 558-605\n  - Referral hook call: lines 595-604\n  - Players passed: lines 600-603 (serialized entries from round data)\n\n- **Atomicity guarantee**: Both calls are inside `db.withTransaction()` — System Invariant 4 compliance\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Claim Handler**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/queue/handlers/referral-claim.ts`\n\n- **Handler function**: `createClaimHandler(deps)` — lines 26-145\n- **Flow**:\n  1. Load claim + idempotency check (lines 40-59)\n  2. Update status to \"processing\" (line 62)\n  3. Re-verify balance (lines 65-81)\n  4. Execute SOL transfer via SystemProgram (lines 83-109)\n  5. Record success/failure (lines 123-129 or 134)\n- **Idempotency**: Skips if already completed or failed (lines 47-5