age; `ReferralClaimCard.tsx` breakdown shows rebates |","+| 3e | Referrer AND referee sees single combined pending balance | SATISFIED | `db.ts:863-883` `getPendingBalance` unified calculation; `ReferralClaimCard.tsx` shows combined balance |"," "," ### FR-4: Referrer Fee Share"," "," | # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |"," |---|-----------|--------|----------|","-| 4a | When a referred player's game settles, the referrer's earning is calculated and stored | GAP | No settlement hook |","-| 4b | Default referrer rate is 1000 bps of the total fee (configurable via environment/config) | GAP | No config env var `REFERRAL_DEFAULT_RATE_BPS` — grep in `config.ts` returns zero matches for \"referral\" |","-| 4c | KOL wallets can have a custom rate set by admin | SATISFIED | `011_referral.sql:78-84`: `referral_kol_rates` table with `rate_bps`, `set_by`, timestamps |","-| 4d | Earnings are recorded per-game in `referral_earnings` with required fields | SATISFIED | `011_referral.sql:28-44`: table has all specified columns |","-| 4e | Referrer earnings accrue indefinitely with no cap or expiry | SATISFIED | No TTL or cap constraint in `011_referral.sql` |","+| 4a | Referrer earning calculated and stored on settlement | SATISFIED | `settle-tx.ts:123-195` `recordReferralEarnings`; `integration.test.ts` verifies amounts |","+| 4b | Default rate is 1000 bps, configurable via env | SATISFIED | `config.ts:95-98` `REFERRAL_DEFAULT_RATE_BPS` default 1000; `settle-tx.ts:147-150` passes to `getReferrerRate` |","+| 4c | KOL custom rate in `referral_kol_rates` | SATISFIED | `011_referral.sql:78-84` creates table; `db.ts:973-978` `getReferrerRate` checks KOL table |","+| 4d | Earnings recorded per-game with all specified columns | SATISFIED | `011_referral.sql:28-44` table with all columns; `db.ts:845-861` `insertReferralEarning` |","+| 4e | Referrer earnings accrue indefinitely with no cap/expiry | SATISFIED | No TTL, cap, or expiry constraint in schema or code |"," "," ### FR-5: Earnings