{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_019TmeLTEYaKAPm7KRv1qWo8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JkEiZq7AJYGJ6Ji4ybffzE","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md","old_string":"- [ ] Route `/r/:code` registered in `App.tsx` <!-- gap: not in App.tsx routes -->\n- [ ] Code stored in localStorage on visit (no auth required) <!-- gap: no localStorage referral code logic -->\n- [ ] Redirect to `/` happens immediately after capture <!-- gap: no route handler -->\n- [ ] On successful authentication, stored code is applied via API <!-- gap: no useReferralApply hook -->\n- [ ] localStorage is cleared after successful apply (or if code is invalid/already linked) <!-- gap: no apply logic -->\n- [ ] Invalid/expired codes show a toast notification, not a blocking error <!-- gap: no error handling -->","new_string":"- [x] Route `/r/:code` registered in `App.tsx` <!-- satisfied: App.tsx:387 <Route path=\"/r/:code\" element={<ReferralCapture />} /> -->\n- [x] Code stored in localStorage on visit (no auth required) <!-- satisfied: App.tsx:460 stores { code, capturedAt } in localStorage key referral_code -->\n- [x] Redirect to `/` happens immediately after capture <!-- satisfied: App.tsx:465 <Navigate to=\"/\" replace /> -->\n- [x] On successful authentication, stored code is applied via API <!-- satisfied: useReferralApply.ts:55 calls applyReferralCode on auth -->\n- [x] localStorage is cleared after successful apply (or if code is invalid/already linked) <!-- satisfied: useReferralApply.ts:57 (success), :73-74 (permanent failure) -->\n- [ ] Invalid/expired codes show a toast notification, not a blocking error <!-- gap: useReferralApply.ts:58 has TODO for toast, uses console.warn instead — no visible user notification -->"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation