{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01X5GHi26rfFgk7b1tM1ksA1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Ppv1EusvVkKhFAy2BTPUmc","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/logs/gap-analysis.log","content":"## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25 (post-completion)\n\nRan: /gap-analysis 300-referral-system --non-interactive\nDate: 2026-03-25\nSpec status: Done\nPrevious analysis: 2026-03-25 (post-iteration-4, 17/90 satisfied)\n\n### Result\n\n| Metric | Count |\n|--------|-------|\n| Total criteria | 90 |\n| SATISFIED | 84 |\n| DEFERRED | 0 |\n| GAP | 6 |\n\n### Gap Summary\n\n| # | FR | Severity | Description |\n|---|-----|----------|-------------|\n| 1 | FR-6 | moderate | Concurrent claims: no DB-level locking on balance snapshot (handler re-verifies, but API route doesn't lock) |\n| 2 | FR-7 | moderate | Rate limiting not applied to /referral/* routes (only on /auth/* and /fairness/*) |\n| 3 | FR-9a | low | Toast notification for invalid/expired codes — useReferralApply.ts uses console.warn |\n| 4 | FR-9f | low | Success toast on referral auto-apply — useReferralApply.ts uses console.warn |\n| 5 | FR-10 | low | referral.game_settled event type defined but never emitted in recordReferralEarnings |\n| 6 | FR-11 | low | Malformed claim payloads throw (retried by queue) instead of being dead-lettered |\n\n### Files Modified\n\n- docs/specs/300-referral-system/gap-analysis.md — full report (overwritten)\n- docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md — FR checkbox annotations updated\n- docs/specs/300-referral-system/history.md — gap analysis entry appended\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":479,"cache_read_input_tokens":118270,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":479,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available